(306, 'Pangdam memberikan ucapan Natal langsung kepada Jemaat GPM Maratha', 'Pangdam give Christmas greeting directly to GPM Maranatha Church', '<p>(Ambon, 25/12). Pangdam XVI/Pattimura, Mayjen TNI Doni Monardo menyempatkan diri memberikan ucapan Selamat Natal langsung kepada ribuan Jemaat Gereja Protestan Maluku(GPM) Maranatha pada Jumat, 25 Des 2015. Kesempatan tersebut diberikan oleh Ketua Sinode Maluku, Pendeta Dr. John Chr. Ruhulessin M.Si saat selesai memimpin ibadah perayaan Natal.</p>\n\n<p>Dalam kesempatan tersebut, Pangdam memberikan ucapan selamat Natal dan mensyukuri Rahmat Tuhan yang begitu besar diberikan kepada masyarakat Maluku berupa kekayaan alam yang melimpah.</p>\n\n<p>Ditempat terpisah, Pangdam juga memberikan ucapan Natal kepada Uskup Amboina, Pastor Mgr. Canisius Mandagi, M.Sc di Keuskupan Maluku.</p>\n\n<p>Pangdam yang didampingi Kasdam dan para pejabat Kodam melanjutkan kegiatan Natalan ke kediaman Wagub Maluku, Ketua DPRD Prov Maluku, Walikota Ambon dan Kabinda. (Pendam16)</p>\n', '<p><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps atn">(</span><span>Ambon</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">25/12</span><span>)</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Regional Commander</span> <span class="hps">XVI</span> <span class="hps">/</span> <span class="hps">Pattimura</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">Maj</span> <span class="hps">Doni</span> <span class="hps">Monardo</span> <span class="hps">took time to</span> <span class="hps">give</span> <span class="hps">Christmas greetings</span> <span class="hps">directly</span> <span class="hps">to thousands</span> <span class="hps">Church</span> <span class="hps">Maluku Protestant Church</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>GPM</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">Maranatha</span> <span class="hps">on Friday</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">25</span> <span class="hps">Dec</span> <span class="hps">2015.</span> <span class="hps">The opportunity</span> <span class="hps">given</span> <span class="hps">by the Chairman of</span> <span class="hps">the Synod of</span> <span class="hps">the Moluccas</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">Rev.</span> <span class="hps">Dr.</span> <span class="hps">John</span> <span class="hps">Chr</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Ruhulessin</span> <span class="hps">M.Si</span> <span class="hps">when completed</span> <span class="hps">lead worship</span> <span class="hps">celebration of Christmas</span><span>.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="hps">On the occasion,</span> <span class="hps">the Regional Commander</span> <span class="hps">congratulated</span> <span class="hps">Christmas</span> <span class="hps">and celebrate</span> <span class="hps">God&#39;s grace</span> <span class="hps">is so</span> <span class="hps">large</span> <span class="hps">Moluccan</span> <span class="hps">community</span> <span class="hps">in the form</span> <span class="hps">given to the</span> <span class="hps">abundant natural resources</span><span>.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="hps">Separately</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">military commander</span> <span class="hps">also</span> <span class="hps">gave</span> <span class="hps">a Christmas greeting</span> <span class="hps">to the Bishop of</span> <span class="hps">Amboina</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">Pastor</span> <span class="hps">Msgr</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Canisius</span> <span class="hps">Mandagi</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">M.Sc</span> <span class="hps">in</span> <span class="hps">Maluku</span> <span class="hps">diocese</span><span>.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="hps">Kasdam</span> <span class="hps">military commander</span> <span class="hps">who was accompanied by</span> <span class="hps">officials</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">military command</span> <span class="hps">continued</span> <span class="hps">Christmas</span> <span class="hps">activities</span> <span class="hps">to the residence of</span> <span class="hps">the Vice Governor</span> <span class="hps">of Maluku</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">Maluku</span> <span class="hps">Province</span> <span class="hps">Chairman of Parliament</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">Mayor of</span> <span class="hps">Ambon</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">Cabinda</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>Pendam16</span><span>)</span></span></p>\n', '492015-12-25_12.15.47.jpg', '2015-12-25 15:04:54', 'Admin', 'Y', NULL, 1, 177, NULL),
